GET /apartments?location=Thessaloniki&min_price=1000&max_price=3000&bedrooms=2&bathrooms=1&pets_allowed=true&amenities=swimming%20pool,oven


# In this example, the endpoint retrieves apartment listings that match the specified search criteria, including location, price range, number of bedrooms and bathrooms,
# pet policies, and amenities. The bedrooms, bathrooms, and pets_allowed parameters are booleans indicating whether the apartment
# should have at least the specified number of bedrooms, bathrooms, or allow pets. The amenities parameter is a comma-separated list of amenities that the apartment must have.